WEBVTT


00:00:18.940 --> 00:00:23.880
♪Only after bloom comes fruit♪

00:00:25.290 --> 00:00:29.260
♪Who says glory must fade to the past♪

00:00:31.920 --> 00:00:37.010
♪Only through thunder
do you reach the clouds♪

00:00:38.210 --> 00:00:43.120
♪Who made you the crown of every peak♪

00:00:44.650 --> 00:00:47.930
♪I stand at the center of the stage♪

00:00:47.930 --> 00:00:51.000
♪My shadow is pinned against the wall♪

00:00:51.710 --> 00:00:56.660
♪Facing the light earns every medal♪

00:00:57.700 --> 00:01:00.880
♪Little birds,
save your needless pecking♪

00:01:00.880 --> 00:01:04.160
♪The open sky rises high♪

00:01:04.700 --> 00:01:09.830
♪When night falls,
the moon begins to shine♪

00:01:10.600 --> 00:01:13.860
♪I stand in the heart of these lands♪

00:01:13.860 --> 00:01:17.220
♪My shadow bears no crown or robe♪

00:01:17.630 --> 00:01:23.300
♪Then I know truth needs no disguise♪

00:01:23.710 --> 00:01:26.960
♪The green hills see me as I am♪

00:01:26.960 --> 00:01:30.290
♪Like dew, lightning,
and moon on the river♪

00:01:30.690 --> 00:01:34.730
♪Showing me exactly who I am♪

00:01:34.730 --> 00:01:35.980
=The Lead=

00:01:36.020 --> 00:01:37.900
=Episode 27=

00:01:38.040 --> 00:01:40.510
♪I don't know♪

00:01:42.510 --> 00:01:44.310
Why is everyone so eager today?

00:01:47.480 --> 00:01:48.840
I think that's our classmate.

00:01:49.840 --> 00:01:50.680
Yi Qing'e.

00:01:51.350 --> 00:01:52.200
Yi Qing'e!

00:01:52.480 --> 00:01:53.840
It really is you!

00:01:54.480 --> 00:01:55.680
What brings you here?

00:01:55.833 --> 00:01:57.359
- When did you get here?
- Zhou Yuzhi.

00:01:57.760 --> 00:01:58.680
Jiahe, Jiahe.

00:02:00.680 --> 00:02:01.560
Chu Jiahe.

00:02:05.400 --> 00:02:06.240
Welcome.

00:02:09.080 --> 00:02:10.870
I saw your performance on stage.

00:02:10.870 --> 00:02:12.280
You sang really well.

00:02:12.280 --> 00:02:13.190
Thank you!

00:02:13.750 --> 00:02:14.680
I'll go practice now.

00:02:16.840 --> 00:02:19.030
Yuzhi, you are classmates?

00:02:19.030 --> 00:02:20.680
- Why not introduce us?
- Exactly.

00:02:20.750 --> 00:02:22.150
Come on, let me introduce you.

00:02:22.190 --> 00:02:23.280
This is Liu Jinsong.

00:02:23.280 --> 00:02:25.030
Wusheng role from Weizhou.

00:02:25.680 --> 00:02:27.030
Chu Jiahe, who is she?

00:02:27.030 --> 00:02:27.870
Yeah.

00:02:28.080 --> 00:02:29.190
An old classmate.

00:02:29.430 --> 00:02:30.960
If there's anything I can do,

00:02:30.960 --> 00:02:32.080
I'll give it my all.

00:02:32.080 --> 00:02:33.870
- You're bragging!
- Get out of here!

00:02:33.870 --> 00:02:35.840
How come you never said that to me?

00:02:35.840 --> 00:02:38.280
What? You judge locals by their looks?

00:02:38.680 --> 00:02:40.280
- What's our local's name?
- Exactly!

00:02:40.280 --> 00:02:41.430
Yi Qing'e.

00:02:42.280 --> 00:02:43.400
Hello, hello.

00:02:43.680 --> 00:02:44.520
I'm Ma Zhiguo.

00:02:44.680 --> 00:02:45.680
Who asked you?

00:02:46.360 --> 00:02:47.200
Shen Yun.

00:02:47.400 --> 00:02:48.240
Come on over.

00:02:49.280 --> 00:02:50.870
She's from Qianzhou County Troupe.

00:02:50.870 --> 00:02:52.030
Also a Guimendan.

00:02:54.240 --> 00:02:55.190
The lead is here.

00:02:55.190 --> 00:02:56.470
Good morning, Lili.

00:02:56.470 --> 00:02:57.360
Morning, Lili.

00:02:57.680 --> 00:02:58.800
- Morning, Lili.
- Hi.

00:02:58.800 --> 00:03:01.080
Why is everyone so pumped today?

00:03:01.680 --> 00:03:03.680
Lili, we have a newcomer.

00:03:03.840 --> 00:03:04.800
She's from Ningzhou.

00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:07.560
No wonder. A newcomer.

00:03:08.630 --> 00:03:09.750
Also from Ningzhou.

00:03:10.870 --> 00:03:12.280
What are you waiting for?

00:03:12.470 --> 00:03:13.870
The newcomer's already practicing.

00:03:13.870 --> 00:03:15.000
Keep up and practice.

00:03:15.310 --> 00:03:16.470
Sure.

00:03:16.590 --> 00:03:18.430
Lili, Gong Lili.

00:03:19.190 --> 00:03:21.120
She's the star of our troupe.

00:03:21.750 --> 00:03:23.030
Keep practicing, everyone.

00:03:23.030 --> 00:03:24.030
You practice first.

00:03:24.030 --> 00:03:25.120
I'll go change.

00:03:25.120 --> 00:03:25.960
Wait a minute.

00:03:28.520 --> 00:03:30.400
Don't you usually do morning practice?

00:03:31.360 --> 00:03:32.630
How should I put it?

00:03:33.400 --> 00:03:34.680
You just don't want

00:03:35.310 --> 00:03:36.910
anyone to see you practice.

00:03:37.360 --> 00:03:38.240
Go ahead and practice.

00:03:38.240 --> 00:03:39.400
I'm going to change.

00:04:14.080 --> 00:04:15.750
Come, stand up, Yi Qin'e.

00:04:15.750 --> 00:04:17.160
Let everyone meet you.

00:04:18.040 --> 00:04:22.510
Qin'e was the deputy leader
of Ningzhou County Troupe.

00:04:22.720 --> 00:04:24.750
She was also a County CPPCC Member.

00:04:25.070 --> 00:04:27.720
She was in Yang Men Nyu Jiang
and Bai She Zhuan.

00:04:28.270 --> 00:04:32.000
Today, she officially joins our troupe.

00:04:32.600 --> 00:04:33.510
Let's welcome her.

00:04:33.870 --> 00:04:35.000
Welcome!

00:04:35.190 --> 00:04:37.480
Welcome, our big star Audrey Hepburn!

00:04:39.270 --> 00:04:40.270
Stop messing around.

00:04:41.160 --> 00:04:42.870
Also, I have an announcement today.

00:04:43.190 --> 00:04:45.120
The You Xi Hu production crew

00:04:45.120 --> 00:04:47.190
is now officially established.

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:48.950
Have a seat. Sit.

00:04:49.870 --> 00:04:51.270
The You Xi Hu project

00:04:51.270 --> 00:04:54.000
is a top priority project
for the province.

00:04:54.000 --> 00:04:55.800
So, today, we have invited

00:04:55.950 --> 00:04:59.190
Directors Gu Cunxiao and Feng Zi.

00:04:59.270 --> 00:05:00.560
They'll be our co-directors.

00:05:00.680 --> 00:05:04.600
Let's invite them to say a few words.

00:05:04.920 --> 00:05:05.760
Alright.

00:05:15.160 --> 00:05:17.160
Let's put on a great show.

00:05:18.360 --> 00:05:20.160
Director Feng, over to you.

00:05:21.160 --> 00:05:22.000
That's it.

00:05:25.240 --> 00:05:26.080
Good.

00:05:27.160 --> 00:05:28.000
Feng Zi.

00:05:32.160 --> 00:05:33.360
Let's work hard together.

00:05:35.600 --> 00:05:36.440
Good.

00:05:38.800 --> 00:05:41.310
The directors' speeches were concise.

00:05:41.310 --> 00:05:42.430
No nonsense at all.

00:05:43.040 --> 00:05:44.750
Now, I'd like to say a few words.

00:05:45.040 --> 00:05:46.240
As you all know,

00:05:46.240 --> 00:05:48.600
for this casting selection,

00:05:48.600 --> 00:05:50.750
we're using a completely new approach.

00:05:51.430 --> 00:05:52.459
We're no longer discussing

00:05:52.470 --> 00:05:54.720
whether there are A/B roles
for Li Huiniang.

00:05:55.040 --> 00:05:58.040
Every Guimendan role in the troupe

00:05:58.750 --> 00:06:00.390
gets a chance to perform.

00:06:00.630 --> 00:06:02.800
You all need to rehearse together

00:06:02.830 --> 00:06:04.190
and compete with each other.

00:06:04.510 --> 00:06:06.920
Whoever fits

00:06:06.920 --> 00:06:08.190
best gets to go first

00:06:08.190 --> 00:06:10.160
as Li Huiniang onstage.

00:06:10.250 --> 00:06:11.120
Got it?

00:06:11.120 --> 00:06:11.960
Yes.

00:06:11.960 --> 00:06:13.000
Got it.

00:06:20.600 --> 00:06:21.870
Look at her movements.

00:06:23.360 --> 00:06:24.310
Look at her.

00:06:24.310 --> 00:06:25.480
That head turn right there

00:06:25.510 --> 00:06:26.360
isn't good enough.

00:06:44.800 --> 00:06:58.120
♪The garden is in full bloom♪

00:07:06.950 --> 00:07:08.830
- Swing your sleeve.
- Right, move forward.

00:07:08.830 --> 00:07:09.892
I'll do this in the front.

00:07:09.903 --> 00:07:11.120
Just add it right after that.

00:07:11.120 --> 00:07:12.920
Put the move right after the line.

00:07:12.920 --> 00:07:14.920
- That's it. Right after it.
- Okay.

00:07:14.920 --> 00:07:16.720
- Or the rhythm drags.
- Okay, no problem

00:07:16.720 --> 00:07:18.390
- Got it? Keep it in mind.
- Okay.

00:07:18.390 --> 00:07:19.570
- Can you remember it?
- Yes.

00:07:19.920 --> 00:07:20.760
Okay.

00:07:20.950 --> 00:07:21.790
Troupe Leader Shan.

00:07:21.830 --> 00:07:23.240
It's about time for today.

00:07:23.240 --> 00:07:24.080
Let's wrap it up.

00:07:24.240 --> 00:07:25.430
Okay, okay.

00:07:25.720 --> 00:07:28.560
All right, we'll stop here for today.

00:07:28.800 --> 00:07:30.310
Same time tomorrow.

00:07:30.390 --> 00:07:31.270
Everyone, be on time.

00:07:31.800 --> 00:07:32.750
All right, that's it.

00:07:33.560 --> 00:07:34.830
Good work, everyone.

00:07:35.560 --> 00:07:36.400
Qin'e.

00:07:36.920 --> 00:07:37.760
Master.

00:07:38.000 --> 00:07:39.573
- Come eat with me.
- See you tomorrow.

00:07:40.000 --> 00:07:41.000
You go eat.

00:07:41.070 --> 00:07:41.920
I'll keep practicing.

00:07:41.920 --> 00:07:43.160
No need to worry about me.

00:07:43.360 --> 00:07:44.240
Remember to eat.

00:07:46.000 --> 00:07:46.840
Qin'e.

00:07:47.040 --> 00:07:49.310
Jiahe and I got a place
in Diaojia Village.

00:07:49.310 --> 00:07:50.270
Let's go to our place

00:07:50.270 --> 00:07:51.630
and make some Saozi noodles.

00:07:51.870 --> 00:07:53.240
Where are you staying?

00:07:53.630 --> 00:07:55.720
Rent in Diaojia Village isn't cheap now.

00:07:56.070 --> 00:07:57.430
We can add a bed for you.

00:07:57.430 --> 00:07:58.430
We can split the rent.

00:07:58.870 --> 00:08:00.510
Hey, Yi Qin'e.

00:08:01.040 --> 00:08:03.270
Let me formally introduce him.

00:08:03.630 --> 00:08:04.470
Director Feng.

00:08:05.270 --> 00:08:06.510
Please introduce yourself.

00:08:06.920 --> 00:08:07.760
I'm Feng Zi.

00:08:07.920 --> 00:08:09.240
Not "Feng" as in crazy,

00:08:09.240 --> 00:08:10.353
but "Feng" as in closed off.

00:08:11.630 --> 00:08:12.870
Welcome to the troupe.

00:08:15.600 --> 00:08:17.160
Artists have their quirks.

00:08:17.390 --> 00:08:20.680
But he is indeed
our first college graduate

00:08:20.750 --> 00:08:22.000
for Qinqiang Opera.

00:08:23.430 --> 00:08:25.720
By the way, are you having any trouble

00:08:25.720 --> 00:08:26.720
with your accommodation?

00:08:27.190 --> 00:08:28.160
No, it's quite good.

00:08:28.160 --> 00:08:29.160
She got assigned a room.

00:08:29.160 --> 00:08:30.480
Tell me if you need help.

00:08:30.680 --> 00:08:33.030
Try your best at the provincial troupe.

00:08:33.790 --> 00:08:36.150
A big stage produces great works.

00:08:36.840 --> 00:08:37.680
Work hard.

00:08:38.346 --> 00:08:39.550
Speak up if you need anything.

00:08:40.910 --> 00:08:41.750
Goodbye.

00:08:43.200 --> 00:08:45.360
The troupe even gave you a room.

00:08:45.440 --> 00:08:47.630
You're really impressive.

00:08:47.750 --> 00:08:49.390
Getting special treatment right away.

00:08:50.960 --> 00:08:52.870
Let's go. Come see our place.

00:08:53.080 --> 00:08:53.920
Let's go.

00:08:55.720 --> 00:08:56.560
Nice shot!

00:08:57.320 --> 00:08:59.270
Scar, is everyone here?

00:08:59.390 --> 00:09:00.910
Why are you so late?

00:09:01.320 --> 00:09:02.480
I got off work ages ago,

00:09:02.480 --> 00:09:04.193
but our dumb director wanted
another look.

00:09:04.910 --> 00:09:06.200
It kept me from making money.

00:09:06.200 --> 00:09:07.040
Come on, come on.

00:09:07.150 --> 00:09:09.030
The street outside our theater

00:09:09.030 --> 00:09:10.320
is full of arts organizations,

00:09:10.390 --> 00:09:13.030
like the acrobatics troupe
and drama troupe.

00:09:13.030 --> 00:09:14.440
They're all here.

00:09:14.600 --> 00:09:16.440
So, this road is called Wenyi Road.

00:09:16.440 --> 00:09:18.000
And this is Diaojia Village.

00:09:20.240 --> 00:09:22.150
We got an even better-looking one today.

00:09:22.440 --> 00:09:23.390
You're so foul-mouthed.

00:09:23.390 --> 00:09:24.510
It'll get you killed one day.

00:09:26.150 --> 00:09:28.000
I'd rather die in your hands.

00:09:35.910 --> 00:09:37.910
Come in! Why stand at the door?

00:09:37.910 --> 00:09:39.320
Hurry, come on in!

00:09:39.320 --> 00:09:40.550
Take a look at our place.

00:09:43.270 --> 00:09:44.390
Your place is so nice.

00:09:44.870 --> 00:09:46.600
I want to move in with you guys.

00:09:50.000 --> 00:09:51.200
I'm serious.

00:09:51.600 --> 00:09:53.000
I really love it here.

00:09:53.630 --> 00:09:54.470
Alright then.

00:09:54.960 --> 00:09:56.120
Let's swap places.

00:09:56.440 --> 00:09:57.550
We'll move to your place.

00:09:57.790 --> 00:09:58.780
You'll move in here.

00:10:00.030 --> 00:10:01.750
Forget about it.

00:10:03.360 --> 00:10:05.030
Let's eat together today.

00:10:06.200 --> 00:10:07.390
You used to be a kitchen maid.

00:10:08.240 --> 00:10:09.600
Cook for us again today.

00:10:11.440 --> 00:10:12.280
Alright.

00:10:27.840 --> 00:10:28.680
Who are you here for?

00:10:30.080 --> 00:10:32.080
I saw you have a room for rent.

00:10:32.080 --> 00:10:34.080
(Mahjong)

00:10:34.080 --> 00:10:34.920
It's rented out.

00:10:34.966 --> 00:10:35.899
Go look somewhere else.

00:10:46.660 --> 00:10:47.900
(Wanted Notice)

00:11:08.820 --> 00:11:10.500
(Hu Sanyuan)

00:11:12.510 --> 00:11:14.440
There's a serial killer in Chang'an.

00:11:14.440 --> 00:11:15.280
Wei Zhenhai.

00:11:15.480 --> 00:11:16.550
We have to be careful.

00:11:17.550 --> 00:11:19.320
You look all sneaky with a mask.

00:11:19.960 --> 00:11:21.630
I got burned before.

00:11:23.870 --> 00:11:25.150
Since when are you the police?

00:11:25.150 --> 00:11:27.480
Protecting Diaojia Village is my duty.

00:11:27.910 --> 00:11:29.240
You're here to rent a place?

00:11:43.320 --> 00:11:46.150
(Diaojia Village Clinic)
It's the lining

00:11:46.150 --> 00:11:48.030
at the end of the rectum,
where the veins

00:11:48.030 --> 00:11:50.390
beneath the skin
have expanded and twisted,

00:11:50.630 --> 00:11:52.670
forming a soft vein mass.

00:11:52.720 --> 00:11:53.670
What does that mean?

00:11:53.790 --> 00:11:54.630
It means hemorrhoids.

00:11:55.390 --> 00:11:56.360
You can't drag this out.

00:11:56.790 --> 00:11:57.840
Shall I remove it?

00:11:58.600 --> 00:12:00.000
Forget it. I'll think it over.

00:12:00.000 --> 00:12:00.840
Du Ziteng.

00:12:01.720 --> 00:12:03.440
How about meds for swelling
and bleeding?

00:12:03.440 --> 00:12:04.320
Du Ziteng.

00:12:06.120 --> 00:12:07.720
How many times have I told you?

00:12:07.840 --> 00:12:09.550
Don't use my full name at the clinic.

00:12:09.550 --> 00:12:11.080
Why can't you remember?

00:12:12.510 --> 00:12:13.870
Fine, Dr. Du.

00:12:14.550 --> 00:12:15.390
What is it?

00:12:16.120 --> 00:12:17.960
Do you still have that spare room
in the back?

00:12:18.200 --> 00:12:19.040
Here's a tenant.

00:12:24.390 --> 00:12:25.550
Take a look.

00:12:26.200 --> 00:12:27.040
This is the room.

00:12:27.610 --> 00:12:29.456
30 a month,
due at the beginning of the month.

00:12:30.840 --> 00:12:31.840
You can cook outside.

00:12:33.510 --> 00:12:34.390
What do you think?

00:12:35.750 --> 00:12:37.790
Can I pay at the end of the month?

00:12:39.150 --> 00:12:40.320
That's the rule here.

00:12:41.270 --> 00:12:42.630
I think I'll pass then.

00:12:43.843 --> 00:12:44.750
What's wrong? Don't go.

00:12:45.750 --> 00:12:46.590
What's wrong?

00:12:48.910 --> 00:12:49.750
What's the matter?

00:12:50.120 --> 00:12:50.960
I didn't touch you.

00:12:51.770 --> 00:12:52.650
What happened?

00:12:52.670 --> 00:12:53.870
I got a stiff neck.

00:12:54.870 --> 00:12:56.240
Come here, let me take a look.

00:12:56.550 --> 00:12:57.400
What are you doing?

00:12:57.480 --> 00:12:58.750
- Let me see.
- What?

00:12:58.750 --> 00:13:00.150
- Here, sit down here.
- What?

00:13:00.240 --> 00:13:01.270
Just let me see.

00:13:01.270 --> 00:13:02.790
- Wait.
- Come on, I can fix it.

00:13:02.910 --> 00:13:04.240
I know. I can fix it.

00:13:04.390 --> 00:13:05.230
Come here.

00:13:05.550 --> 00:13:06.390
Here, right?

00:13:07.510 --> 00:13:08.350
Come on.

00:13:11.750 --> 00:13:13.510
Hei, find a thick stick.

00:13:14.790 --> 00:13:15.840
Isn't it just a room?

00:13:15.840 --> 00:13:16.910
There's no need for this.

00:13:17.240 --> 00:13:18.080
Hei.

00:13:18.630 --> 00:13:19.960
Hei, what are you doing?

00:13:20.750 --> 00:13:22.270
- No, no!
- Why are you yelling?

00:13:22.270 --> 00:13:23.270
He's helping you.

00:13:23.390 --> 00:13:24.670
Don't move! Stay still!

00:13:25.480 --> 00:13:26.630
No, no.

00:13:26.870 --> 00:13:28.510
- Right here, right?
- Yes, yes.

00:13:32.360 --> 00:13:33.840
Head down. Down, down.

00:13:40.200 --> 00:13:41.040
How is it?

00:13:47.720 --> 00:13:48.560
Amazing.

00:13:49.320 --> 00:13:50.600
I didn't know you had this skill.

00:13:50.630 --> 00:13:51.550
Impressive, huh?

00:13:52.480 --> 00:13:53.480
That's my buddy.

00:13:53.550 --> 00:13:55.870
He's a 3rd-gen bone-setting expert.

00:13:56.030 --> 00:13:57.320
You two are in the same field.

00:13:57.320 --> 00:13:58.270
Why else would I

00:13:58.280 --> 00:13:59.320
bring him here?

00:14:00.206 --> 00:14:01.475
Why didn't you say that earlier?

00:14:01.600 --> 00:14:03.120
My buddy keeps a low profile.

00:14:03.120 --> 00:14:04.360
He wouldn't let me tell you.

00:14:04.910 --> 00:14:05.750
I'll be going then.

00:14:05.930 --> 00:14:06.790
No, no.

00:14:06.840 --> 00:14:07.680
You can stay here.

00:14:07.870 --> 00:14:09.390
You can pay at the month's end.

00:14:09.910 --> 00:14:10.910
That doesn't seem right.

00:14:10.910 --> 00:14:11.910
It'd break your rules.

00:14:12.320 --> 00:14:13.440
It's settled, then.

00:14:16.440 --> 00:14:17.280
Buddy.

00:14:18.550 --> 00:14:20.000
What exactly do you do?

00:14:20.440 --> 00:14:21.310
Why?

00:14:21.390 --> 00:14:23.240
Look, I have an idea.

00:14:23.480 --> 00:14:25.390
You can practice here when you're free.

00:14:25.600 --> 00:14:27.600
You set your own rates for treatments.

00:14:27.600 --> 00:14:28.600
I'll take half.

00:14:29.120 --> 00:14:29.960
Thirty-seventy.

00:14:30.090 --> 00:14:30.960
Forty-sixty.

00:14:30.960 --> 00:14:31.800
Deal.

00:14:35.480 --> 00:14:37.080
Same taste as in Ningzhou.

00:14:37.840 --> 00:14:39.000
You're amazing.

00:14:41.080 --> 00:14:41.920
Qin'e,

00:14:43.270 --> 00:14:44.790
you've worked in the kitchen for years.

00:14:46.270 --> 00:14:47.550
Who taught you this,

00:14:47.550 --> 00:14:48.630
Master Song or Master Liao?

00:14:53.960 --> 00:14:54.800
Both of them.

00:14:55.390 --> 00:14:56.510
Who cooks better?

00:14:59.240 --> 00:15:00.080
I think

00:15:00.080 --> 00:15:01.253
Qin'e's cooking is the best.

00:15:11.790 --> 00:15:13.330
I'm full. I'll get going.

00:15:14.790 --> 00:15:16.080
I'll walk you out.

00:15:29.600 --> 00:15:30.550
You're going too far.

00:15:31.240 --> 00:15:33.670
We're not in Ningzhou anymore.

00:15:33.910 --> 00:15:35.080
You're the B role.

00:15:35.600 --> 00:15:37.270
She's just an extra.

00:15:37.720 --> 00:15:38.910
What's there to worry about?

00:15:42.120 --> 00:15:43.226
I'm not as easygoing as you.

00:15:43.480 --> 00:15:44.870
I won't let her take my spot.

00:15:46.630 --> 00:15:47.630
Then stop bringing up

00:15:47.630 --> 00:15:49.080
that old, dusty stuff.

00:15:50.030 --> 00:15:51.250
She's had it rough.

00:15:57.510 --> 00:15:58.480
Who hasn't?

00:15:59.140 --> 00:16:01.620
(Diaojia Village)

00:16:04.910 --> 00:16:05.760
Once rumors like this

00:16:05.790 --> 00:16:06.630
start spreading,

00:16:06.630 --> 00:16:08.270
who knows how they'll end up?

00:16:08.750 --> 00:16:10.120
You're still young.

00:16:10.630 --> 00:16:12.720
Your reputation
for the rest of your life...

00:16:14.070 --> 00:16:14.910
Master Song!

00:16:14.910 --> 00:16:15.776
They said the new chef

00:16:15.787 --> 00:16:17.349
- forced himself on you.
- Master Song!

00:16:17.360 --> 00:16:18.910
She said you were taken advantage of.

00:16:19.320 --> 00:16:20.270
What did he do to you?

00:16:20.550 --> 00:16:21.790
- Master Song!
- Don't shout.

00:16:21.840 --> 00:16:23.282
- Master Song!
- I'll warm you up.

00:16:23.293 --> 00:16:23.800
It's cold.

00:16:23.960 --> 00:16:25.150
Master Song saved you.

00:16:26.120 --> 00:16:27.550
Then Chu Jiahe ruined your name.

00:16:29.510 --> 00:16:30.870
Play a straight.

00:16:30.910 --> 00:16:32.480
Don't play that. Play this!

00:16:32.480 --> 00:16:34.440
Just stay out of it.

00:16:34.440 --> 00:16:35.390
If I listened to you,

00:16:35.480 --> 00:16:36.870
I'd be covered in paper slips.

00:16:36.870 --> 00:16:38.720
If you did, you'd have won by now.

00:16:38.720 --> 00:16:40.080
You play a straight.

00:16:42.000 --> 00:16:43.270
- You're back.
- Come here.

00:16:43.320 --> 00:16:44.160
An Ace.

00:16:44.480 --> 00:16:46.240
Qin'e, you're back.

00:16:48.496 --> 00:16:49.480
You finally got off work.

00:16:49.480 --> 00:16:50.840
Why are you back so late?

00:16:50.840 --> 00:16:51.680
Come on.

00:16:56.630 --> 00:16:57.480
Is your hand okay?

00:16:58.670 --> 00:17:00.840
The floor's covered in dirt.

00:17:01.440 --> 00:17:03.320
We'll need to cover it later.

00:17:04.350 --> 00:17:06.030
Take your stuff. I don't want it.

00:17:07.030 --> 00:17:07.870
What's wrong?

00:17:08.400 --> 00:17:09.270
Are you upset?

00:17:10.070 --> 00:17:11.110
Did rehearsal go badly?

00:17:11.400 --> 00:17:12.640
None of your business.

00:17:13.400 --> 00:17:15.030
How is it none of my business?

00:17:15.640 --> 00:17:17.160
Your stuff is my concern.

00:17:17.590 --> 00:17:19.830
There are so many things to tidy.

00:17:19.960 --> 00:17:21.070
I don't know you that well.

00:17:21.790 --> 00:17:22.880
Not that well?

00:17:24.000 --> 00:17:25.680
We came all the way from Ningzhou.

00:17:26.000 --> 00:17:26.840
Right?

00:17:27.160 --> 00:17:28.750
What more do you want?

00:17:29.680 --> 00:17:30.520
Fine.

00:17:30.830 --> 00:17:31.670
Then tell me.

00:17:32.030 --> 00:17:33.830
What's the name on my ID?

00:17:34.310 --> 00:17:35.160
When is my birthday?

00:17:35.170 --> 00:17:36.550
What do I hate? What do I like?

00:17:44.110 --> 00:17:44.960
I don't know.

00:17:44.970 --> 00:17:45.840
Take your stuff.

00:17:46.030 --> 00:17:46.870
No.

00:17:47.920 --> 00:17:48.760
I won't.

00:17:49.700 --> 00:17:50.653
Does any of that matter?

00:17:51.680 --> 00:17:52.520
What your name is,

00:17:52.680 --> 00:17:53.560
how old you are,

00:17:53.560 --> 00:17:54.420
and what you like...

00:17:54.420 --> 00:17:55.770
None of that matters at all.

00:17:56.750 --> 00:17:57.590
To me,

00:17:58.640 --> 00:17:59.480
these things

00:18:00.830 --> 00:18:02.440
don't stop me from liking you at all.

00:18:04.440 --> 00:18:06.240
Ever since I first saw you on stage,

00:18:07.720 --> 00:18:08.560
I knew

00:18:09.590 --> 00:18:10.510
that you're the one

00:18:10.880 --> 00:18:11.860
for the rest of my life.

00:18:26.000 --> 00:18:27.070
You can't throw this away.

00:18:27.750 --> 00:18:28.920
It's a good pot. Why toss it?

00:18:28.920 --> 00:18:29.543
No, you can't.

00:18:29.554 --> 00:18:30.710
Or you can't relieve yourself

00:18:30.720 --> 00:18:31.845
- at night.
- Give it to me!

00:18:31.856 --> 00:18:32.960
Creep! Get lost!

00:18:32.960 --> 00:18:34.640
How is this creepy?

00:18:39.720 --> 00:18:42.790
You pranked me, huh?

00:18:42.790 --> 00:18:44.440
Sticking paper strips all over my face.

00:18:44.440 --> 00:18:45.290
Now, look at you,

00:18:45.290 --> 00:18:46.920
got kicked out by your girl.

00:18:47.590 --> 00:18:48.880
Who are you yelling at?

00:18:48.960 --> 00:18:50.480
Your wife also scolds you.

00:18:50.830 --> 00:18:52.270
Girls are just like that.

00:18:52.270 --> 00:18:54.350
I'll coax her, and she'll be fine.

00:18:56.790 --> 00:18:58.070
Look at those paper slips,

00:18:58.070 --> 00:18:59.160
and you're acting cocky?

00:18:59.680 --> 00:19:00.790
Do you still want this?

00:19:00.920 --> 00:19:02.310
Of course. Why wouldn't I?

00:19:02.680 --> 00:19:04.880
A new liner will make it a new one.

00:19:05.000 --> 00:19:06.640
You want a freebie, huh?

00:19:06.640 --> 00:19:08.920
Fine, clean this place up,

00:19:08.960 --> 00:19:09.980
or the kids will get cut.

00:19:10.240 --> 00:19:11.080
Go play now.

00:19:11.880 --> 00:19:12.750
Hurry up, hurry up.

00:19:15.200 --> 00:19:16.040
Why are you

00:19:16.160 --> 00:19:17.510
getting so much water?

00:19:19.030 --> 00:19:21.830
- (Liu Hongbing is like a hot coal.)
- Qin'e.

00:19:22.310 --> 00:19:24.510
- (However far Yi Qin'e throws him,)
- You rest.

00:19:24.720 --> 00:19:27.400
- (he always rolls back with heat.)
- I'll be back.

00:19:28.160 --> 00:19:30.930
- (Hot and annoying.)
- You haven't eaten yet.

00:19:31.190 --> 00:19:32.856
- (Hu Sanyuan said)
- What can I get you?

00:19:32.899 --> 00:19:33.880
(that the biggest trait)

00:19:33.880 --> 00:19:35.200
(of this kind of man)

00:19:35.510 --> 00:19:36.750
(is)

00:19:37.270 --> 00:19:38.720
(unreliable.)

00:19:44.960 --> 00:19:45.800
Qin'e.

00:19:48.750 --> 00:19:49.590
Qin'e?

00:19:52.510 --> 00:19:54.030
Why are your eyes red? Are you crying?

00:19:54.480 --> 00:19:55.320
No.

00:19:55.750 --> 00:19:56.640
I just fell asleep.

00:19:59.920 --> 00:20:01.880
How was the first day of rehearsal?

00:20:03.000 --> 00:20:03.840
Normal.

00:20:06.960 --> 00:20:08.110
What does that mean?

00:20:09.030 --> 00:20:09.870
It means

00:20:11.110 --> 00:20:12.270
nothing is abnormal.

00:20:18.440 --> 00:20:19.380
Did Liu Hongbing come?

00:20:23.510 --> 00:20:25.880
I found a place to stay
in Diaojia Village.

00:20:26.160 --> 00:20:27.173
Let's check it out later.

00:20:29.270 --> 00:20:30.480
I'll go get Master,

00:20:30.790 --> 00:20:32.270
so we can rehearse.

00:20:39.240 --> 00:20:43.920
♪This love remains as strong as steel♪

00:20:45.680 --> 00:20:50.440
♪Even if a blade severs my head♪

00:20:53.200 --> 00:21:06.920
♪It can't sever my love for Pei♪

00:21:10.720 --> 00:21:12.400
I went to watch their rehearsal today.

00:21:13.830 --> 00:21:15.270
The A role's singing

00:21:15.440 --> 00:21:17.160
is way different from our county's.

00:21:18.750 --> 00:21:19.636
Is it better or worse?

00:21:19.920 --> 00:21:21.070
Hard to say.

00:21:21.480 --> 00:21:22.680
Their vocal style is different.

00:21:22.680 --> 00:21:23.520
A different school.

00:21:24.550 --> 00:21:26.030
What school?

00:21:26.270 --> 00:21:27.790
The provincial troupe is now aiming

00:21:27.920 --> 00:21:29.640
for a modern and trendy vocal style.

00:21:30.310 --> 00:21:32.640
They even added
Western bel canto singing.

00:21:33.070 --> 00:21:33.920
Just wait.

00:21:34.000 --> 00:21:35.000
They might even add

00:21:35.030 --> 00:21:37.240
Western drums and a Western horn.

00:21:37.750 --> 00:21:38.590
What is this?

00:21:39.000 --> 00:21:41.270
It's a total disgrace to our profession.

00:21:41.920 --> 00:21:42.806
Can you tolerate that?

00:21:43.590 --> 00:21:44.430
We haven't tried it.

00:21:44.720 --> 00:21:45.806
It might actually be great.

00:21:45.880 --> 00:21:46.790
Great, my foot.

00:21:48.110 --> 00:21:49.160
You call the shots.

00:21:49.920 --> 00:21:50.760
Let's continue.

00:22:01.030 --> 00:22:02.550
(At the provincial troupe,)

00:22:02.550 --> 00:22:04.680
(training had to be kept secret.)

00:22:05.350 --> 00:22:07.720
(After Yi Qin'e arrived in Chang'an,)

00:22:07.720 --> 00:22:08.640
(it took her days)

00:22:08.790 --> 00:22:10.310
(to finally figure it out.)

00:22:11.110 --> 00:22:12.750
(It seemed that suffering in public)

00:22:12.750 --> 00:22:14.640
(made you look inferior.)

00:22:15.000 --> 00:22:16.350
(It had to be done in secret)

00:22:16.590 --> 00:22:18.240
(to be seen as valuable.)

00:22:18.940 --> 00:22:19.830
(She felt)

00:22:19.830 --> 00:22:21.720
(that people were afraid
that their clumsy,)

00:22:21.720 --> 00:22:23.240
(sweaty, worn-out look)

00:22:23.510 --> 00:22:27.000
(of hard practice would be seen,)

00:22:28.240 --> 00:22:29.510
(and that the fact of ending up)

00:22:29.750 --> 00:22:31.790
(with nothing after all the effort
would be mocked.)

00:22:32.240 --> 00:22:35.310
(She didn't get why they saw it
that way,)

00:22:35.640 --> 00:22:36.510
(but she knew)

00:22:36.920 --> 00:22:38.640
(she had to learn to fit in.)

00:22:52.750 --> 00:22:54.550
She sang off-key,

00:22:55.880 --> 00:22:57.400
and she still had the nerve to laugh.

00:23:01.860 --> 00:23:05.380
(Rehearsal Hall)

00:23:10.640 --> 00:23:12.160
Yesterday's outfit looked pretty good.

00:23:14.400 --> 00:23:15.240
What's up?

00:23:15.480 --> 00:23:31.110
♪My tears ran like blood♪

00:23:32.960 --> 00:23:40.350
♪With my head down,
I cursed the heavens♪

00:23:40.400 --> 00:23:48.680
♪Since Pan Renmei was born♪

00:23:48.680 --> 00:23:51.270
♪I should never have been born♪

00:23:53.740 --> 00:23:56.620
♪A man who cheats
the ruler must be beheaded♪

00:23:56.620 --> 00:23:59.700
♪If the ruler cheats his men,
don't serve him♪

00:23:59.700 --> 00:24:02.580
♪If folks break the law,
let the law decide♪

00:24:02.580 --> 00:24:05.540
♪If officials wrong the people,
take it to court♪

00:24:05.540 --> 00:24:08.300
♪Sons who wrong their fathers die young♪

00:24:08.300 --> 00:24:11.060
♪Sons wronged by their fathers run away♪

00:24:11.060 --> 00:24:13.740
♪How can a wife oppress her husband♪

00:24:13.740 --> 00:24:16.300
♪A true man lives with dignity♪

00:24:16.300 --> 00:24:17.740
♪The emperor rules all♪

00:24:17.740 --> 00:24:19.020
♪Only the Xus are second to him♪

00:24:19.020 --> 00:24:20.380
♪The emperor rules all♪

00:24:20.380 --> 00:24:21.620
♪It's ruled half by his court♪

00:24:21.620 --> 00:24:22.820
♪This realm belongs to me♪

00:24:22.820 --> 00:24:24.180
♪No need to consult you♪

00:24:24.180 --> 00:24:25.500
♪Your realm was built♪

00:24:25.500 --> 00:24:26.900
♪By our families♪

00:24:41.030 --> 00:24:43.160
I won't stay in this dump anyway.

00:24:43.480 --> 00:24:44.360
Hongbing.

00:24:44.487 --> 00:24:45.300
Hongbing,

00:24:45.310 --> 00:24:46.510
you left your stuff inside.

00:24:49.350 --> 00:24:50.423
Put it on.

00:24:53.200 --> 00:24:54.510
Go tell Li Laosi

00:24:54.510 --> 00:24:56.000
that he's not my buddy anymore.

00:24:56.830 --> 00:24:59.400
Hongbing, Manager Li is at a meeting.

00:24:59.680 --> 00:25:01.000
Come on, don't give me that.

00:25:01.000 --> 00:25:02.362
Besides, not letting you stay here

00:25:02.373 --> 00:25:03.640
wasn't even his idea.

00:25:03.640 --> 00:25:04.830
It wasn't his idea?

00:25:04.830 --> 00:25:05.750
Well, if it wasn't...

00:25:07.110 --> 00:25:07.950
What did you say?

00:25:29.880 --> 00:25:32.030
Noodles need garlic for full flavor.

00:25:33.510 --> 00:25:34.750
Who are you?

00:25:35.070 --> 00:25:36.920
You don't know me, but I know you.

00:25:37.720 --> 00:25:39.500
You're the provincial troupe's
lead drummer.

00:25:42.510 --> 00:25:43.750
My niece

00:25:44.030 --> 00:25:45.270
is in the same troupe as you.

00:25:45.830 --> 00:25:46.670
Her name is Yi Qin'e.

00:25:46.880 --> 00:25:47.720
She's new.

00:25:49.030 --> 00:25:50.920
The young girl from the County Troupe?

00:25:51.000 --> 00:25:51.840
Yes, exactly.

00:25:53.440 --> 00:25:55.310
Please look out for her in the future.

00:25:56.550 --> 00:25:57.880
I'm just a drummer.

00:25:57.880 --> 00:25:58.960
How can I look out for her?

00:25:59.920 --> 00:26:01.000
Others might not know,

00:26:01.000 --> 00:26:01.840
but I know that.

00:26:02.510 --> 00:26:05.400
Every beat you strike drives the play.

00:26:06.550 --> 00:26:07.880
You strike at its backbone.

00:26:08.030 --> 00:26:09.920
You strike at the play's soul.

00:26:11.440 --> 00:26:12.750
You're quite the expert.

00:26:13.070 --> 00:26:14.240
What exactly do you do?

00:26:19.880 --> 00:26:21.200
Right here, here. Yes, exactly.

00:26:21.640 --> 00:26:22.480
Hu,

00:26:23.270 --> 00:26:24.110
you know what?

00:26:24.440 --> 00:26:25.590
The way you pound my back

00:26:25.590 --> 00:26:29.550
feels like the Double Drumsticks
in opera.

00:26:30.160 --> 00:26:31.270
It even has beats.

00:26:32.680 --> 00:26:35.480
Opera, our bones,
and life all have beats.

00:26:36.000 --> 00:26:38.240
A hard hit might not get a reaction.

00:26:39.550 --> 00:26:42.920
A light tap might leave a loud echo.

00:26:44.720 --> 00:26:47.200
Lost wealth will always return.

00:26:47.960 --> 00:26:49.880
Paths always cross in life.

00:26:51.070 --> 00:26:53.310
If we hit at the right beat
for the right tune,

00:26:53.510 --> 00:26:54.480
the play will be right.

00:26:56.000 --> 00:26:57.070
Is this a lesson

00:26:57.070 --> 00:26:57.910
about drums or life?

00:26:58.640 --> 00:27:00.126
It depends on what you want to learn.

00:27:00.270 --> 00:27:01.356
What would I learn from you?

00:27:01.790 --> 00:27:03.070
Just kidding. Lie down.

00:27:03.070 --> 00:27:05.376
I'm the Northwest Drum King.
Why should I learn from you?

00:27:07.240 --> 00:27:08.680
Then we're acquainted now.

00:27:09.000 --> 00:27:10.680
When you're worn out, come by.

00:27:10.680 --> 00:27:11.960
I'll give you a massage.

00:27:12.200 --> 00:27:13.270
Folks in your line of work

00:27:13.270 --> 00:27:14.400
get these work aches.

00:27:14.480 --> 00:27:15.400
The frozen shoulder

00:27:16.030 --> 00:27:17.510
and the chill in your joints...

00:27:17.720 --> 00:27:19.030
I can work it all out.

00:27:19.880 --> 00:27:21.400
You'll feel much better right away.

00:27:22.750 --> 00:27:24.276
Wow, you've got skills.

00:27:24.287 --> 00:27:26.125
Not bad, huh?
Your shoulder must feel lighter.

00:27:26.136 --> 00:27:27.510
You mixed Qinqiang Opera

00:27:27.510 --> 00:27:28.570
with back-tapping massage.

00:27:29.160 --> 00:27:30.000
How much is it?

00:27:30.730 --> 00:27:31.590
Where's my money?

00:27:31.590 --> 00:27:32.920
Next time. Next time.

00:27:32.920 --> 00:27:34.270
Oh, that's so awkward.

00:27:34.270 --> 00:27:35.200
It's fine. It's fine.

00:27:35.350 --> 00:27:36.400
Then don't worry.

00:27:36.400 --> 00:27:38.070
I'll take care of your niece.

00:27:38.110 --> 00:27:38.950
Don't worry.

00:27:39.060 --> 00:27:39.960
Thanks. Thanks.

00:27:39.960 --> 00:27:41.030
Alright, come again.

00:27:41.030 --> 00:27:42.120
- No problem.
- Good.

00:27:42.240 --> 00:27:43.310
I'll pay you next time.

00:27:43.830 --> 00:27:45.510
I just don't like taking advantage.

00:27:46.620 --> 00:27:47.480
Going to the restroom.

00:27:47.480 --> 00:27:48.640
That felt pretty good.

00:27:55.720 --> 00:27:56.790
Come on, easy now.

00:27:57.310 --> 00:27:59.160
Watch your step.

00:27:59.160 --> 00:28:00.000
Easy, easy.

00:28:02.440 --> 00:28:04.880
Listen, I heard this miracle doctor here

00:28:05.030 --> 00:28:06.440
can help with back-tapping massage.

00:28:07.270 --> 00:28:08.110
Du.

00:28:08.920 --> 00:28:10.070
Come on, take a look.

00:28:10.200 --> 00:28:12.310
Her lower back hurts.
She can't stand straight.

00:28:13.000 --> 00:28:13.840
Back-tapping massage.

00:28:14.110 --> 00:28:15.350
Come in, come in.

00:28:15.640 --> 00:28:16.750
I'm getting old.

00:28:17.590 --> 00:28:19.070
I often tweak my back.

00:28:19.440 --> 00:28:20.720
I just moved a table

00:28:21.830 --> 00:28:22.720
and tweaked it.

00:28:24.070 --> 00:28:24.920
Does this spot hurt?

00:28:25.310 --> 00:28:26.150
Not really.

00:28:26.590 --> 00:28:27.430
How about here?

00:28:27.640 --> 00:28:28.680
A little.

00:28:29.440 --> 00:28:30.300
It hurts.

00:28:30.310 --> 00:28:31.790
Come here, come here.

00:28:32.310 --> 00:28:33.400
It's an old back injury.

00:28:35.070 --> 00:28:37.350
Girl, why's your back so bad?

00:28:39.270 --> 00:28:40.966
You run your stall earlier than I do

00:28:40.977 --> 00:28:42.110
and close it later than I do.

00:28:42.110 --> 00:28:43.350
What's the point?

00:28:44.310 --> 00:28:45.150
It hurts.

00:28:46.750 --> 00:28:48.270
Just trying to earn a bit more.

00:28:49.880 --> 00:28:51.460
I heard that in the past,

00:28:51.510 --> 00:28:53.550
when the old
Third Front factory disbanded,

00:28:53.550 --> 00:28:55.510
the state assigned you a job.

00:28:55.680 --> 00:28:56.520
I didn't take it.

00:28:57.070 --> 00:28:58.160
I took the severance buyout.

00:28:59.270 --> 00:29:01.030
Doesn't that mean more money?

00:29:01.160 --> 00:29:02.310
Why run a stall with us?

00:29:02.640 --> 00:29:03.720
I gave it to my kid.

00:29:04.880 --> 00:29:06.160
Your kid isn't around?

00:29:06.160 --> 00:29:07.000
Are you living alone?

00:29:08.440 --> 00:29:09.280
No.

00:29:11.550 --> 00:29:12.750
Don't worry about the rest.

00:29:12.920 --> 00:29:14.920
I'll take you home when we're done here.

00:29:15.000 --> 00:29:17.160
I'll pack up your stall for you tonight.

00:29:17.920 --> 00:29:18.760
Thank you.

00:29:20.110 --> 00:29:21.510
Doctor, you keep tapping.

00:29:21.790 --> 00:29:23.030
I'll wait for her outside.

00:29:38.240 --> 00:29:40.000
Your tapping is quite steady.

00:29:42.920 --> 00:29:44.270
It's like a drumbeat.

00:29:56.110 --> 00:29:56.950
What's wrong?

00:30:18.880 --> 00:30:19.790
Turn around.

00:30:28.440 --> 00:30:29.400
Take off your mask.

00:30:45.240 --> 00:30:46.550
When did you learn this skill?

00:30:48.350 --> 00:30:49.920
Back in the day,

00:30:50.350 --> 00:30:51.960
I had free time when I was inside.

00:30:56.960 --> 00:30:58.160
Doctor, why did you stop?

00:30:59.550 --> 00:31:00.390
All done.

00:31:01.400 --> 00:31:02.720
No, it still needs some work.

00:31:06.310 --> 00:31:07.680
I shouldn't do it for too long.

00:31:10.200 --> 00:31:11.040
Let's go.

00:31:12.070 --> 00:31:12.960
Are you feeling better?

00:31:13.030 --> 00:31:14.200
Yes, I can stand up straight.

00:31:14.200 --> 00:31:15.186
Does it feel comfortable?

00:31:15.640 --> 00:31:17.110
I told you he's good.

00:31:18.510 --> 00:31:19.350
How is it?

00:31:19.590 --> 00:31:20.430
Great.

00:31:21.030 --> 00:31:22.560
Awesome. How much is it?

00:31:23.240 --> 00:31:24.080
Ten yuan.

00:31:24.510 --> 00:31:25.350
No need.

00:31:26.880 --> 00:31:28.400
No, really, I don't need it.

00:31:28.790 --> 00:31:29.630
Here.

00:31:29.750 --> 00:31:31.110
We'll talk next time.

00:31:31.400 --> 00:31:33.400
You must come back. Once isn't enough.

00:31:33.400 --> 00:31:35.200
You need a few more sessions.

00:31:35.830 --> 00:31:36.920
When will you come back?

00:31:37.790 --> 00:31:38.630
Tomorrow?

00:31:40.550 --> 00:31:41.510
In a couple of days.

00:31:42.720 --> 00:31:43.720
Which day exactly?

00:31:43.720 --> 00:31:45.400
How about the day after tomorrow?

00:31:46.880 --> 00:31:47.790
We'll see.

00:31:49.790 --> 00:31:50.880
We're leaving, Doctor.

00:31:52.550 --> 00:31:53.530
Let's pack up the stall.

00:31:53.640 --> 00:31:54.480
Alright.

00:32:14.640 --> 00:32:15.480
Jiahe,

00:32:16.070 --> 00:32:17.310
a while ago,

00:32:17.440 --> 00:32:19.200
you bought a trench coat
at Luoma Market.

00:32:19.270 --> 00:32:20.920
Can I borrow it?

00:32:22.240 --> 00:32:23.110
What for?

00:32:23.640 --> 00:32:24.920
Going on another blind date?

00:32:25.590 --> 00:32:26.830
What blind date?

00:32:26.920 --> 00:32:29.070
All the good men are already taken.

00:32:29.440 --> 00:32:30.480
None left for me.

00:32:32.150 --> 00:32:33.240
I'm going to the movies.

00:32:33.550 --> 00:32:34.920
There's a new release.

00:32:35.440 --> 00:32:36.750
I heard everyone who saw it

00:32:36.750 --> 00:32:38.640
cried their eyes out in the theater.

00:32:39.640 --> 00:32:40.960
Why don't you come with me?

00:32:41.310 --> 00:32:42.830
There's enough sadness in life.

00:32:42.830 --> 00:32:44.400
Why go to the theater for more?

00:32:45.880 --> 00:32:48.200
What? Just because of Yi Qin'e?

00:32:48.920 --> 00:32:50.350
Do you have to be like this?

00:32:51.960 --> 00:32:53.400
Ever since she got here,

00:32:53.590 --> 00:32:56.000
you've been tense.

00:32:56.440 --> 00:32:57.880
You mope around all day,

00:32:57.880 --> 00:32:59.110
or you just practice.

00:32:59.240 --> 00:33:00.920
Are you obsessed or something?

00:33:01.790 --> 00:33:02.630
You don't understand.

00:33:04.350 --> 00:33:06.160
True, I don't get it.

00:33:06.873 --> 00:33:07.960
If you want to be the lead,

00:33:07.960 --> 00:33:09.640
go compete with Gong Lili.

00:33:09.790 --> 00:33:11.790
Why stare at Yi Qin'e all day?

00:33:42.830 --> 00:33:43.670
Hey, girl.

00:33:44.110 --> 00:33:45.680
Dancing alone is no fun.

00:33:45.800 --> 00:33:46.640
I'll dance with you.

00:33:46.640 --> 00:33:47.480
Are you crazy?

00:33:47.960 --> 00:33:49.790
Tell me what's bothering you.

00:33:49.880 --> 00:33:51.200
I'll help you forget your worries.

00:33:51.940 --> 00:33:52.840
Don't go.

00:33:54.110 --> 00:33:55.310
- What?
- You're so fierce.

00:33:55.310 --> 00:33:56.680
Come here, have a drink with me.

00:33:56.680 --> 00:33:57.680
Come on, come here.

00:33:57.790 --> 00:33:59.030
Such a temper. Come here.

00:33:59.030 --> 00:34:00.150
- Let go!
- Sit right here.

00:34:00.270 --> 00:34:01.110
Come on.

00:34:01.350 --> 00:34:02.190
Come on!

00:34:02.480 --> 00:34:03.320
Don't move!

00:34:04.480 --> 00:34:05.320
Come on.

00:34:08.670 --> 00:34:09.563
Don't come any closer!

00:34:09.960 --> 00:34:12.070
Why are you so fierce?

00:34:12.600 --> 00:34:14.360
Come on, stab me right here.

00:34:14.790 --> 00:34:16.760
Make me bleed. Come on.

00:34:16.760 --> 00:34:17.600
Bro, what's going on?

00:34:17.760 --> 00:34:18.670
None of your business.

00:34:18.670 --> 00:34:19.510
Get lost.

00:34:19.630 --> 00:34:20.920
This girl is pretty tough.

00:34:21.000 --> 00:34:21.880
She's from the troupe.

00:34:22.070 --> 00:34:23.440
She's usually like this.

00:34:25.960 --> 00:34:27.110
Pretty tough.

00:34:28.000 --> 00:34:28.840
Come on, stab me.

00:34:28.840 --> 00:34:29.920
Come on!

00:34:30.550 --> 00:34:32.150
Why are you here?

00:34:32.710 --> 00:34:34.030
I've been looking for you.

00:34:35.480 --> 00:34:36.320
She's my sister.

00:34:36.760 --> 00:34:37.760
She fought with our mom

00:34:38.000 --> 00:34:39.320
and came here acting crazy.

00:34:39.320 --> 00:34:40.710
She should know where this is.

00:34:40.840 --> 00:34:41.680
Right, right.

00:34:42.030 --> 00:34:43.550
We're leaving now. Let's go.

00:34:43.550 --> 00:34:44.390
Stop right there.

00:34:44.760 --> 00:34:46.110
You're not leaving.

00:34:48.150 --> 00:34:49.000
Yeah.

00:34:49.280 --> 00:34:50.840
Let me apologize to you guys.

00:34:51.630 --> 00:34:54.070
My sister ruined the mood for you.

00:34:54.070 --> 00:34:56.230
Drinks are on me today.

00:34:56.320 --> 00:34:58.920
Keep the music going and have fun.

00:34:59.030 --> 00:34:59.870
What a loser.

00:34:59.940 --> 00:35:00.790
Get lost.

00:35:00.800 --> 00:35:02.510
Sorry, my apologies to you guys.

00:35:02.660 --> 00:35:03.500
Let's go.

00:35:03.590 --> 00:35:04.676
Stop embarrassing yourself.

00:35:04.800 --> 00:35:05.640
Move.

00:35:06.250 --> 00:35:07.110
It's fine now.

00:35:07.110 --> 00:35:08.660
It's all good. Let's keep dancing.

00:35:09.070 --> 00:35:10.030
Why are you pulling me?

00:35:10.710 --> 00:35:11.550
Let go of my hand.

00:35:12.320 --> 00:35:13.160
Let go.

00:35:13.630 --> 00:35:14.470
Let go of me.

00:35:16.000 --> 00:35:17.710
Why act so tough, little girl?

00:35:18.880 --> 00:35:20.030
If I hadn't covered for you,

00:35:20.240 --> 00:35:21.280
you'd be done for by now.

00:35:21.280 --> 00:35:22.269
Who do you think you are

00:35:22.280 --> 00:35:23.120
to butt in?

00:35:25.800 --> 00:35:27.513
If you weren't
from the provincial troupe,

00:35:28.070 --> 00:35:29.440
I wouldn't even talk to you.

00:35:29.760 --> 00:35:31.110
You investigated me?

00:35:31.840 --> 00:35:33.400
The guy inside was your buddy, right?

00:35:33.630 --> 00:35:34.590
Playing the hero now?

00:35:35.230 --> 00:35:36.400
You men are all the same.

00:35:36.630 --> 00:35:37.510
You all want the same.

00:35:37.840 --> 00:35:38.680
What's with the act?

00:35:40.960 --> 00:35:42.400
I must be bored out of my mind.

00:35:43.510 --> 00:35:45.070
You girls these days,

00:35:45.280 --> 00:35:46.320
one after another,

00:35:46.510 --> 00:35:48.280
are all so hard to handle.

00:35:50.070 --> 00:35:50.960
Listen.

00:35:51.710 --> 00:35:52.710
I already have a wife.

00:35:53.000 --> 00:35:54.670
My wife is an angel.

00:35:55.670 --> 00:35:56.510
Get lost.

00:35:56.630 --> 00:35:57.670
Go hang with my buddy.

00:36:03.070 --> 00:36:04.800
(Pay phone)
Where will you sleep tonight?

00:36:05.000 --> 00:36:06.480
On the street. Where else?

00:36:07.440 --> 00:36:08.760
Stop worrying about me.

00:36:09.190 --> 00:36:10.510
I'm on my own either way.

00:36:11.480 --> 00:36:13.150
I just don't get it, Mom.

00:36:13.280 --> 00:36:14.920
Why is this so hard to do?

00:36:15.590 --> 00:36:16.800
The old man can easily

00:36:16.800 --> 00:36:18.480
transfer me to the Beishan office.

00:36:18.480 --> 00:36:19.880
He just doesn't want to help.

00:36:20.440 --> 00:36:22.030
Listen, she's just an actress.

00:36:22.840 --> 00:36:25.000
You're hurting our bond now.

00:36:28.190 --> 00:36:30.760
I've made up my mind about my own life.

00:36:31.400 --> 00:36:32.240
Don't worry.

00:36:32.380 --> 00:36:33.240
That's it.

00:36:33.360 --> 00:36:34.200
Hongbing.

00:37:12.880 --> 00:37:14.320
See you tomorrow.

00:37:32.030 --> 00:37:32.870
Who are you here for?

00:37:33.400 --> 00:37:34.240
Uncle,

00:37:35.510 --> 00:37:36.440
I'm here for you.

00:37:36.480 --> 00:37:37.440
You're the one I need.

00:37:37.480 --> 00:37:39.150
- Why so formal?
- Here for me?

00:37:39.150 --> 00:37:41.840
Here, eat the Rou Jia Mo while it's hot.

00:37:42.480 --> 00:37:43.320
Take it away.

00:37:43.710 --> 00:37:45.280
Don't try this with me. I'm telling you.

00:37:45.520 --> 00:37:46.400
I'm not kidding.

00:37:46.400 --> 00:37:47.800
- Eat it now.
- Take it away.

00:37:47.800 --> 00:37:49.280
Troupe Leader, why are you here?

00:37:53.840 --> 00:37:55.320
He's so thick-skinned.

00:38:03.480 --> 00:38:04.360
It's all fat.

00:38:04.550 --> 00:38:21.030
♪Crying for the brothers♪

00:38:22.670 --> 00:38:23.550
Hurry up.

00:38:24.480 --> 00:38:25.360
Okay, okay.

00:38:25.510 --> 00:38:26.350
Okay.

00:38:37.030 --> 00:38:37.920
Try harder.

00:38:40.960 --> 00:38:41.800
Who's he here for?

00:38:47.720 --> 00:38:48.590
Recently,

00:38:48.710 --> 00:38:49.960
Master Chen from the courtyard

00:38:49.960 --> 00:38:51.400
taught me an awesome vocal trick.

00:38:51.400 --> 00:38:52.400
Let me show you.

00:38:56.800 --> 00:38:58.320
It really is you.

00:38:58.880 --> 00:39:00.070
Why is it you?

00:39:00.360 --> 00:39:02.190
Stop playing dumb.

00:39:02.760 --> 00:39:04.230
You followed me all the way here.

00:39:04.230 --> 00:39:05.110
What do you want?

00:39:05.590 --> 00:39:07.840
Who do you think you are?

00:39:08.110 --> 00:39:09.760
You think you're a swan, huh?

00:39:10.110 --> 00:39:12.110
I'm here looking for Yi Qin'e.

00:39:12.320 --> 00:39:13.670
Are you Yi Qin'e?

00:39:14.000 --> 00:39:15.400
- Get your paws off.
- Crazy.

00:39:15.880 --> 00:39:17.280
What do you want with Yi Qin'e?

00:39:17.920 --> 00:39:18.840
Who let you in?

00:39:19.590 --> 00:39:21.550
The first pot of meat
from Zhuba Market today.

00:39:22.280 --> 00:39:23.120
Have a taste.

00:39:23.510 --> 00:39:24.630
Is it really the first pot?

00:39:25.190 --> 00:39:26.190
You bet.

00:39:28.070 --> 00:39:29.190
Don't just eat it yourself.

00:39:29.190 --> 00:39:30.670
Share it with everyone.

00:39:31.360 --> 00:39:32.710
Come if you haven't had breakfast.

00:39:34.030 --> 00:39:34.960
Come on.

00:39:34.960 --> 00:39:36.110
Have some Mo. Eat up.

00:39:38.440 --> 00:39:39.760
Let me introduce myself.

00:39:39.800 --> 00:39:41.360
I'm Yi Qin'e's friend.

00:39:42.550 --> 00:39:45.280
Take good care of Qin'e from now on.

00:39:45.360 --> 00:39:46.710
- Sure.
- I'll share plenty of Mo.

00:39:46.710 --> 00:39:48.230
Right, okay, okay.

00:39:48.230 --> 00:39:49.070
What are you doing?

00:39:50.960 --> 00:39:51.800
Master Gu,

00:39:53.150 --> 00:39:55.150
I saw you act in Beishan before.

00:39:56.000 --> 00:39:56.840
You were amazing.

00:39:57.190 --> 00:39:58.030
Who are you?

00:39:58.800 --> 00:40:00.440
I'm Qin'e's friend.

00:40:00.800 --> 00:40:03.440
I brought her all the way from Ningzhou.

00:40:04.280 --> 00:40:05.120
Have a seat.

00:40:06.840 --> 00:40:07.840
We're rehearsing here.

00:40:08.000 --> 00:40:09.360
You shouldn't be here.

00:40:09.590 --> 00:40:10.430
Get out.

00:40:10.840 --> 00:40:11.680
No problem.

00:40:12.030 --> 00:40:13.400
Come on, have some Mo.

00:40:13.510 --> 00:40:14.350
Leave.

00:40:14.550 --> 00:40:15.390
Okay.

00:40:21.400 --> 00:40:22.306
Morning, Director Feng.

00:40:25.110 --> 00:40:26.150
This is the director?

00:40:27.360 --> 00:40:28.200
Who are you?

00:40:28.840 --> 00:40:30.190
I'm Yi Qin'e's friend.

00:40:30.920 --> 00:40:33.400
I brought Qin'e here from Ningzhou.

00:40:36.150 --> 00:40:37.360
Let me ask you.

00:40:37.550 --> 00:40:39.630
Of all the troupes in the country,

00:40:39.630 --> 00:40:40.670
which one

00:40:40.670 --> 00:40:42.400
allows eating in the rehearsal hall?

00:40:43.590 --> 00:40:44.760
No discipline at all.

00:40:47.110 --> 00:40:47.950
Who let you...

00:40:51.320 --> 00:40:52.190
Go ask the janitor.

00:40:52.800 --> 00:40:53.840
Why did they let him in?

00:40:54.030 --> 00:40:55.000
Okay, Director Feng.

00:40:57.190 --> 00:40:58.400
Still eating?

00:40:58.670 --> 00:41:00.150
Desperate for meat, huh?

00:41:01.360 --> 00:41:02.670
He's not my boyfriend.

00:41:02.880 --> 00:41:04.320
Why are you telling me this?

00:41:07.840 --> 00:41:09.590
You didn't want me
at the provincial troupe.

00:41:10.190 --> 00:41:11.190
Neither did I.

00:41:13.800 --> 00:41:14.640
That's enough.

00:41:14.920 --> 00:41:16.710
Stop gloating when you've won.

00:41:18.270 --> 00:41:19.110
In this world,

00:41:19.110 --> 00:41:20.760
you can't have every good thing.

00:41:21.230 --> 00:41:22.840
I might not want what you think is good.

00:42:10.230 --> 00:42:11.070
Alright, stop.

00:42:11.733 --> 00:42:12.800
That wasn't even a minute.

00:42:12.800 --> 00:42:14.190
I've been practicing.

00:42:14.440 --> 00:42:16.280
It's not time for the show yet, is it?

00:42:16.630 --> 00:42:17.470
What's the rush?

00:42:17.880 --> 00:42:19.670
It'll be too late by then.

00:42:20.873 --> 00:42:22.182
The duration of the Woyu posture

00:42:22.193 --> 00:42:23.440
must be at least three minutes.

00:42:23.440 --> 00:42:25.920
How does this move build the character?

00:42:26.030 --> 00:42:27.320
Does it have to be three minutes?

00:42:27.670 --> 00:42:28.760
Can't we cut it down a bit?

00:42:28.840 --> 00:42:29.840
That's so rigid.

00:42:30.320 --> 00:42:31.160
What?

00:42:31.920 --> 00:42:32.760
Rigid?

00:42:36.000 --> 00:42:38.190
Kid, let me tell you.

00:42:38.400 --> 00:42:41.760
Woyu is the soul of this scene.

00:42:43.110 --> 00:42:44.110
It's the soul!

00:42:44.630 --> 00:42:46.440
The successful actors of the past

00:42:46.710 --> 00:42:49.360
were good at singing and skills.

00:42:49.920 --> 00:42:52.960
It's the slight differences in details

00:42:53.190 --> 00:42:56.960
that decided who became the lead.

00:42:57.760 --> 00:42:58.600
Do you understand?

00:42:58.960 --> 00:43:01.880
Master Gu, the lead era is over.

00:43:01.920 --> 00:43:03.550
We're the new generation of actors.

00:43:05.020 --> 00:43:06.940
=The Lead=
(Preview)

00:43:12.880 --> 00:43:13.720
With your condition,

00:43:13.970 --> 00:43:15.539
you need bed rest for at least 3 months.

00:43:15.550 --> 00:43:17.840
Yi Qin'e can totally handle the B role.

00:43:17.920 --> 00:43:19.110
What do you think?

00:43:19.110 --> 00:43:21.360
Let's see what she's made of.

00:43:21.360 --> 00:43:22.200
Look at this setup.

00:43:22.440 --> 00:43:24.280
It instantly looks so classy.

00:43:25.070 --> 00:43:26.400
Picking locks? Are you a thief?

00:43:26.840 --> 00:43:29.000
It's the art of war. It's a strategy.

00:43:29.480 --> 00:43:30.550
Later, take this with you

00:43:30.670 --> 00:43:31.580
to the rehearsal hall.

00:43:31.800 --> 00:43:32.640
What?

00:43:37.000 --> 00:43:41.620
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

00:43:43.090 --> 00:43:47.930
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

00:43:49.370 --> 00:43:53.560
♪We met and brushed past♪

00:43:55.120 --> 00:44:02.420
♪Your shadow drifted out of sight♪

00:44:16.790 --> 00:44:20.540
♪The stove fire blazed in my dream♪

00:44:22.140 --> 00:44:27.710
♪Lit up the tracks of pearly tears♪

00:44:28.830 --> 00:44:32.890
♪In my dream, water sleeves flew♪

00:44:34.020 --> 00:44:39.610
♪Hiding a lifetime of love♪

00:44:40.770 --> 00:44:44.970
♪The Qinling Mountains
crossed the stage♪

00:44:46.010 --> 00:44:51.640
♪Spring water brewed strong wine♪

00:44:52.810 --> 00:44:57.500
♪Sheep moved through the valley♪

00:44:58.180 --> 00:45:03.350
♪It felt like a promise
from another life♪

00:45:04.020 --> 00:45:09.050
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

00:45:10.080 --> 00:45:15.510
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

00:45:15.890 --> 00:45:21.170
♪If I chose again, I'd still roam♪

00:45:22.120 --> 00:45:27.930
♪All over this sunlit plateau♪

00:45:27.930 --> 00:45:33.350
♪The dream ends; the curtain falls♪

00:45:33.900 --> 00:45:39.410
♪Moonlight washes off this stage makeup♪

00:45:39.960 --> 00:45:44.920
♪The one in the mirror wears gray hair♪

00:45:45.940 --> 00:45:51.220
♪Already sang all my joy and sorrow♪

00:45:52.020 --> 00:46:01.050
♪Already shouted across Qinchuan Plain♪